      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, budget-friendly option for a daily driver. Mechanically, the engine starts and runs consistently, though it lacks the smoothness of a newer model and may require some routine maintenance soon. The transmission shifts through all gears, but you might notice occasional hesitation during acceleration. Cosmetically, the exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and fading paint in certain areas. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows wear on the upholstery and some of the plastic trim. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and minor cosmetic imperfections.",
