      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled distinction. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the most exacting standards, this motorcar offers an uncompromising experience for the discerning enthusiast. We invite you to acquire this pristine example of engineering excellence, which stands as a testament to superior care and mechanical stewardship.",
      "price": 46500.0,
