    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is honestly in absolute showroom condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. Not a single scratch, dent, or worry to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
