    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s M-Division engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 powerhouse, a high-compression inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a speed-sensitive variable M differential lock, ensuring surgical precision through the apex. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement, a full VANOS overhaul, and structural subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains tight, and the factory finish is free of any clear coat failure or road rash. A truly turn-key, collector-grade specimen for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
